file.name: ValueExamples.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: 'test'
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /content:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: 'test'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  stringExample:
                    type: string
                    example: 'stringValue'
                  numberExample:
                    type: number
                    example: 123
                  booleanExample:
                    type: boolean
                    example: true
                  objectExample:
                    type: object
                    example:
                      key: 'objectValue'
                  arrayExample:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: string
                    example:
                      - 'arrayValue'
